#: ../../source/UserGuide/tool/mcp_session.rst:15
msgid "**后台任务管理** - 维护异步会话线程实现非阻塞通信"
msgstr "**Background Task Management** - Maintain asynchronous session threads to implement non-blocking communication"

#: ../../source/UserGuide/tool/mcp_session.rst:16
msgid "**异常安全断开** - 处理通信错误时自动执行清理操作"
msgstr "**Exception-Safe Disconnect** - Automatically performs cleanup operations when handling communication errors."

