#: ../../source/UserGuide/tool/mcp_session.rst:105
msgid "当设置 persistent_link=True 时，会话在退出异步上下文管理器后不会自动断开。 在这种模式下，用户必须显式调用 disconnect() 来释放网络连接与后台任务。 否则可能导致 资源泄露（例如挂起的会话协程、未释放的 socket 连接等）。"
msgstr "When persistent_link=True is set, the session will not automatically disconnect after exiting the asynchronous context manager. In this mode, the user must explicitly call disconnect() to release the network connection and background tasks. Otherwise, it may lead to resource leaks (such as pending session coroutines, unreleased socket connections, etc.)."
